chapters.title: Chapter 10:  A Blazing Beacon
chapters.info:
Lady Birgitte Trahelion,
      p. 271–272 (320)—Captain-General of the Queen's Guards under
      Elayne, and her Warder.  She tells everyone she is
      from Kandor.  However she is actually the Birgitte
      from the stories.
      See
      Birgitte.
